    <h2>What we write for White Lake families</h2>
    <p>White Lake is a lake-and-rec community, and the policies that work here look different from a standard subdivision policy. We have carriers who understand lake homes, waterfront structures, and recreational watercraft:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong><a href="../personal/auto-insurance/">Auto insurance</a></strong> — Michigan No-Fault with PIP options that work for White Lake households. Multi-vehicle, teen drivers, trucks and SUVs that tow boats and trailers.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="../personal/home-insurance/">Home insurance</a></strong> — lakefront, lake-access, and inland homes throughout 48383 and 48386. We size Coverage B (Other Structures) correctly for docks, boathouses, hoists, seawalls, and detached garages.</li>
      <li><strong>Boat, pontoon, jet ski, personal watercraft</strong> — for White Lake, Pontiac Lake, Cedar Island Lake, Long Lake, Williams Lake, Lakeville Lake, and beyond. Standalone marine policies usually beat the boat rider on a homeowners policy on both price and limits.</li>
      <li><strong>Flood insurance</strong> — important to evaluate for lakefront and low-lying parcels. We can pull a flood quote and walk you through whether you need it.</li>
      <li><strong>Umbrella</strong> — extra liability over your auto, home, and watercraft. Especially important when you have a dock that hosts guests and a boat that hosts passengers.</li>
      <li><strong>Recreational vehicles</strong> — RVs, travel trailers, ATVs, side-by-sides, and snowmobiles. Pontiac Lake Rec Area and Indian Springs Metropark sit right here, so we write a lot of these.</li>
      <li><strong>Classic and collector car</strong> — strong classic-car community in the area. We're a Hagerty agency.</li>
      <li><strong><a href="../personal/life-insurance/">Life insurance</a></strong> — term, whole, and universal life. Independent so we can shop carriers based on your health, age, and goals.</li>
      <li><strong>Condo, renters, vacant property</strong> — and anything else you need.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-2">For White Lake business owners</h2>
    <p>From small businesses along Highland Road and M-59 to contractors and lake-service businesses throughout western Oakland County, we write commercial coverage through 35+ markets:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>General liability, commercial property, BOP</li>
      <li><a href="../business/workers-compensation/">Workers compensation</a></li>
      <li>Commercial auto for service vehicles and fleets</li>
      <li>Contractor coverage — builders, HVAC, electrical, plumbing, landscaping, dock builders, lawn care</li>
      <li>Marine and dock-service businesses</li>
      <li>Professional liability and errors &amp; omissions</li>
      <li>Restaurants, bars, and retail</li>
      <li>Cyber liability, surety bonds, and builders risk</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-2">Why White Lake residents choose an independent agent</h2>
    <p>Lake homes, lakefront properties, multiple watercraft, and rural acreage don't fit cookie-cutter policies from captive agents. As an independent agency we represent <a href="../carriers/">35+ carriers</a> including specialty markets for lake homes, waterfront structures, and marine coverage. We shop every renewal and switch you to whichever carrier offers the best fit and value.</p>

